quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Do you see the one who denies the Judgment
  107,2,They are those who repulse the orphan
  107,3,And do not encourage the feeding of the indigent
  107,4,So woe to the worshippers
  107,5,Who are neglectful of their prayers
  107,6,Those who want to be seen
  107,7,But refuse to do even neighborly deeds